{"tid":1663380,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"[即時] 係人嘅就即刻轉場大埔","createTime":"2019-10-19T11:22:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-19T11:36:46.000Z","uid":61002,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"55a7eb00a03792e18a054f99463bee060faf2bf4","tid":1663380,"uid":61002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T11:22:05.000Z","msg":"A. <br />\n13 分鐘前<br />\n識人做Popo<br />\n兇手去咗大埔狗屋自殺<br />\n黑警唔想做condom就告鳩佢謀殺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nFact check 咗未？<br />\n消息來源係同一總區嘅Popo<br />\n以往咁多次冇單料係流<br />\n<br />\n但新聞未出街前繼續要跟進<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nbtw係自首 自隊一打膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nB. <br />\n新富區社區主任胡耀昌：<br />\n「隧道斬人兇徒證實已自首（fact checked with PPRB），我現前往威爾斯醫院了解傷者情況。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/MaxWuND/posts/2437674299824673\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FMaxWuND%2Fposts%2F2437674299824673&d=om99xhx1cOxPLv9Q%2FbR%2FoITtxWFByFwd8BqLGIwhgUE%3D&h=216195a5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/MaxWuND/posts/2437674299824673</a><br />\n<br />\n#新聞"},{"pid":"1323e90480601713d4ca66d7eb65e0839a8adf47","tid":1663380,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T11:22:23.000Z","msg":"【1020 尖咀見】真。遊行指南參考<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <a href=\"https://lih.kg/aksjJwU\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/aksjJwU</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbcb81dcf671f6df38dd3ca569720c0fdacfdd21","tid":1663380,"uid":12251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T11:22:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d82c088ccbff463aeae9989c0e6580a07cb9ce31","tid":1663380,"uid":124180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T11:25:52.000Z","msg":"自首=尋求黑警保護安全送回關口過關"},{"pid":"152fff9d7084c6c6bb1d875998987130a0ec601b","tid":1663380,"uid":268123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T11:35:11.000Z","msg":"【香城施政報告2019】群策群力 轉危為機<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1656908\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1656908</a><br />\n<br />\n<em><strong>政治問題</strong></em><br />\n<br />\n- 重塑公民身分戶口政策保障國家、香港安全和利益<br />\n- 取消18區區議會、建立地域市政議會<br />\n- 禁止公務人員在任前、任內和任後獲港外榮典<br />\n- 改善高鐵一地兩檢操作方式<br />\n<br />\n<em><strong>便民基建</strong></em><br />\n<br />\n- 興建東鐵、西鐵快速線並完善輕鐵和西鐵聯乘關係<br />\n- 完善機場集體運輸並加強機場、港珠澳大橋協同發展<br />\n- 修正港鐵、巴士可加可減機制<br />\n<br />\n[i]<strong>醫療、教育方向</strong>[i]<br />\n<br />\n- 興建至少四所新區域全科醫院<br />\n- 以減少送院為目標的社區護理服務<br />\n- 重塑教育, 著重知識、技能層次分工<br />\n<br />\n求正評及幫推！"},{"pid":"d0195570b3576a254eda0c2ed823af25efbaef89","tid":1663380,"uid":18948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T11:36:46.000Z","msg":"自首同自殺爭好遠呀清<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}